Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.96,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(365,357)}Negotiation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:08.02,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,466)\fad(400,1000)\c&HE0E0E0&}20th December - 11:50 am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I actually came to Japan on a top secret mission, {\alpha&HFF&}so if you could refrain from mentioning to the Japanese police that... err..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I actually came to Japan on a top secret mission, so if you could refrain from mentioning to the Japanese police that... err..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone that I've met you... {\alpha&HFF&}including my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone that I've met you... including my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone to know that I've encountered the FBI either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my father were to find out, L would definitely be informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even suspect me slightly, {\alpha&HFF&}and now this incident will be dismissed as a mere accident by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:01:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even suspect me slightly, and now this incident will be dismissed as a mere accident by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? What's with the big sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was caught up in a random bus hi-jacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus hi-jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A criminal, who attempted to rob a bank two days ago, decided to try his luck at a bus hi-jacking this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's a scary place these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just happened to be on that bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the culprit jumped off the bus and ended up being hit by an oncoming car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That culprit... did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have time to see things right through to the end though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:01:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if that wasn't just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... you were investigating someone when you got on that bus, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And somehow, a criminal has ended up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, {\alpha&HFF&}I know that you were a brilliant FBI investigator, but right now, you're just my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know that you were a brilliant FBI investigator, but right now, you're just my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to remember that you're no longer an investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I won't get involved in the Kira-case."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I won't do anything dangerous."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me those things before coming here, and that's why I brought you with me, so we can visit your parents in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Ray. It's just a habit.. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Ray. It's just a habit.. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Sorry, you don't need to worry about it that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we start a family, you'll be too busy to remember what it was like to be an investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have the time to slip into old habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:03:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you've got to help me think of a way to impress your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna write the name of the agent you've just identified?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. {\alpha&HFF&}It'll be a week before I'll write his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. It'll be a week before I'll write his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he were to die immediately after encountering me, it'd look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for me to wait till his investigation progresses further, and allow him the opportunity to investigate as many people connected to the police as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I'll bait L with some more prisoners...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}there's been another victim that's left some sort of suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, there's been another victim that's left some sort of suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send me the images.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, did you know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me that Shinigami actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, tell the police to continue surveying the prisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may see more prisoners leaving notes behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:08.06,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}27th December - 3:00 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's pretty busy around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where it's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally I'll be able to show you the results of the investigations and experiments I've been carrying out these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of the Death Note, I've been able to identify several different methods of killing people by utilizing some of the local criminals as my test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:37.96,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(622,173)}Accidental Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:37.96,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(446,246)\fad(500,0)}26th December              8:30 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:37.96,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(446,321)\fad(500,0)}Run over by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cause of death and any further details are written in the Death Note first, and the name is added afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.96,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(341,165)\fad(1000,0)}Hanekuroda
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person will still die exactly as it is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeh? Even I hadn't realized that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray Penber-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around, and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you even think about turning around or putting your hands in your pockets I'll kill you instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait... This voice... I've heard it before.. somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll prove to you that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see that cafe over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a guy wearing glasses working there. I'm going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I should at least kill one person for you to take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man has a record of physically abusing women, but due to lack of evidence he's never been convicted for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only right that those who cause suffering to society should receive judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that L's told you that I'm only able to kill people if I know their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, I can kill anyone who's around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got any requests, just go ahead and ask. I'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you're Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'm sure that it'd be much more painful for you to lose someone dear to you than to lose anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to consider that person as the one really being held hostage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Not her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. {\alpha&HFF&}I've done some research on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. I've done some research on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go against any of my orders, I'll kill everyone. Including your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you've brought your laptop with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have all the files of all the investigators assigned to Japan on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to work, I've always got my laptop with me, {\alpha&HFF&}but I don't have any of those files.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to work, I've always got my laptop with me, but I don't have any of those files.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please take this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, take out the transceiver and put the ear piece on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A transceiver? This is practically a toy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, this way, there'll be no record of communication, and even underground, as long as we're close enough, we'll be able to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's thought this through...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, please get on the Yamanote line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether you take the inside or the outside track.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be constantly observing you from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while you are on the train, look straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember that I can kill you at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've boarded, sit at a corner seat by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there isn't one free, we'll wait until there is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you several questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get an answer that completely conflicts with my expectations, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll kill your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get an answer that completely conflicts with my expectations, I'll kill your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many FBI agents have entered Japan, and how are they organized?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer quietly into the transceiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there are twelve of us, divided into four teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, take out the contents of the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to write the name of your direct superior, who should have all the names of the investigators, in the top box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? {\alpha&HFF&}What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I've got no choice but to do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he only has their names, he shouldn't be able to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'd like you to open up your laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your superior should be sending you some files soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be the files containing the names and faces of all FBI agents that have entered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like before, I want you to write each name in a box while concentrating on each of their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, what are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've finished your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please place the papers and the transceiver back into the original envelope, and leave it on the wire rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've done that, remain on the train for a further 30 minutes without moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, once you're sure that no one will notice you leaving the envelope, disembark the train at a station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... {\alpha&HFF&}why can't I remember whose voice this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... why can't I remember whose voice this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:58.78,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}4:41 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... {\alpha&HFF&}Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye... {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye... Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The papers Ray Penber wrote on were torn out pages from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, he killed his own teammates without even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Penber's superior died after sending the files to all members of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the investigators on the team died of a heart attack after receiving those files.
Comment: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}you've got a call from the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, you've got a call from the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just heard that all our investigators that we sent to Japan have been found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them died of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only assume that they must have been killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have to do this, L, {\alpha&HFF&}but we're going to have to cut off our investigations in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have to do this, L, but we're going to have to cut off our investigations in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Yagami is on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}I've just spoken to the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, I've just spoken to the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you've been using the FBI to investigate us and those who are connected with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean to say that you actually suspected us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that it was a necessity in order to narrow down Kira's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't treat your allies as spies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't trust L after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this means that Kira must have killed FBI agents too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will kill anyone who opposes them, even if the person isn't a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is a real monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another prisoner who has left a suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only eat apples
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray is..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! {\alpha&HFF&}He was killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He was killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this "family meeting" about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I tried to hide it, you'd all eventually find out, so I'll tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently heading the investigation into Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Wow, you're really amazing, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the start of my problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, yesterday, {\alpha&HFF&}twelve FBI agents that were sent to Japan to investigate Kira.. all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, yesterday, twelve FBI agents that were sent to Japan to investigate Kira.. {\alpha&HFF&}all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, yesterday, twelve FBI agents that were sent to Japan to investigate Kira.. all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean they were all killed by Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to put it bluntly, if I go after Kira, I may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most horrific crime I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of my staff are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should quit as well, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. Your life is far more important than your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way I'm stepping down from this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There's no way I'm stepping down from this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not bow to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's very honorable of you, father. I'm very proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything happens to you... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll make sure that Kira will be sentenced to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything happens to you... I'll make sure that Kira will be sentenced to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is willing to kill those who oppose them even if they aren't criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could all be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to think of your lives, families and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who wants to leave is free to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you there'll be no risk of demotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those of you who have the conviction to fight Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}even if you have to sacrifice all the things I've just mentioned, should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those of you who have the conviction to fight Kira, even if you have to sacrifice all the things I've just mentioned, should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember him telling everyone to get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't remember the rest of the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? {\alpha&HFF&}I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I understand. {\alpha&HFF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my thinking is correct... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira may have been among those passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my thinking is correct... Kira may have been among those passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, {\alpha&HFF&}I should be able to use this bus as a route to get to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I should be able to use this bus as a route to get to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six people, including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}In fact, I'd like to think of it as six people willing to stand up to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. In fact, I'd like to think of it as six people willing to stand up to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to trust the six of you who have shown yourselves to have a great sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L may have just said that he trusts us, {\alpha&HFF&}but we don't trust L!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L may have just said that he trusts us, but we don't trust L!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}we've all decided to put our lives on the line to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, we've all decided to put our lives on the line to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know what that means!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you've only ever given orders without revealing your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't work with someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}if you're serious about joining forces with us to catch Kira, will you come here and join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, if you're serious about joining forces with us to catch Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}will you come here and join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, if you're serious about joining forces with us to catch Kira, will you come here and join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said that I would trust you.
