Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he asking for our support now, at the risk of exposing himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that he's solved countless cases on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be able to solve this one on his own too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, judging by his past actions, we may end up dealing with a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake, huh? Could be possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to trust L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that L's skills will be invaluable to us in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's said from the start that this case would require the cooperation of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it conceivable that... {\alpha&HFF&}L was actually waiting for this to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it conceivable that... L was actually waiting for this to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"For this to happen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were people on the case, right from the start, who were suspicious of L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People were resigning left, right and center, and information was somehow being leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been impossible for him to command the investigation with trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean L's been waiting until only those dedicated individuals he could trust, and whom are willing to stand against evil remained at headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, if you're going to join forces with L, I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't try to follow any of you, or try to find L.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose to trust L and work alongside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently in a room at the Teitou hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be switching between hotels in the city every few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to request that my hotel room be used as the real headquarters during this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to these stipulations, I'd like you to split into two groups, and, leaving a gap of at least 30 minutes between the two, come up to my room before midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}right now it seems that we are moving towards each other at an even rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, right now it seems that we are moving towards each other at an even rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll expose myself as L, in front of people, for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find out about this, {\alpha&HFF&}I can guarantee that you'll try to move in on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find out about this, I can guarantee that you'll try to move in on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done quite a lot over the last few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to think hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make any mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I proceed from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real battle starts now, L!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
